				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13444984/scp-5270#post-4719837</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 15 Jul 2020 05:12:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>As a general note, object class is based on difficulty of containment, not potential for danger. We have a fair number of cute and harmless SCP entities that are Keter class, simply because they're very difficult to contain.</p> 
				 	]]>
