					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It’s me! The person who wrote the containment procedures. I’m incredibly impressed and pleased with how this turned out! My inclusion of .aic BEARHUGGER was born out of the largest failure of this community: Not enough ursine articles. When I first wrote the conprocs, I was imagining a small wooden bear, but I adore what <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gerrymanderbassist" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2346106&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592764059" alt="GerrymanderBassist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2346106)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gerrymanderbassist" >GerrymanderBassist</a></span> did.</p> <p>&lt;3 Penguin</p> 
				 	]]>
