				<wikidot:authorName>GerrymanderBassist</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2346106</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks to the following wonderful people for crit:</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blackmagicfine" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3357293&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592762506" alt="BlackMagicFine" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3357293)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/blackmagicfine" >BlackMagicFine</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2199269&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592762506" alt="Yossipossi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2199269)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" >Yossipossi</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sharpembrace" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6032914&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592762506" alt="SharpEmbrace" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6032914)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sharpembrace" >SharpEmbrace</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguepjp" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5813664&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592762506" alt="PlaguePJP" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5813664)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguepjp" >PlaguePJP</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/advocate" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3248547&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592762506" alt="Advocate" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3248547)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/advocate" >Advocate</a></span></p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1989312&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592762506" alt="Doctor Fullham" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1989312)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" >Doctor Fullham</a></span> for inspiring the title.</p> <p>Thanks to Bandit &quot;Nickname Changes&quot; Bebop for creating the wonderful sprites I used for this article.</p> <p>Please hug your local bear.</p> <p>This article took a while, but I'm glad I took my time. Corpsecon was fun!</p> 
				 	]]>
